=== Review ===
One of the most popular FFA/Duel maps in Red Eclipse, Abuse has a simple, fairly small, yet well balanced layout reminiscent of Quake. A teleporter makes the map feel smaller than it is.

=== Notes & Strategies ===

* You can throw mines through the portals to catch unsuspecting foes.
* The rocket spawns on top of the central diagonal platform.